# 1.コンテナ起動
```
docker compose up -d
```

# 2.コンテナ内bash
```
docker compose exec app bash
```

# 3.ビルド
```
cd app

sh gradlew build

OR

sh gradlew build --continuous

java -jar build/libs/app-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar
```

http://localhost:8080/

